# Implementation Plan - Repo Integration

The goal is to test three cloned repositories (`anime-downloader`, `moviebox-api`, `bazarr-movies`) individually and then integrate them into the `backend` folder.

## User Review Required
> [!WARNING]
> `anime-downloader` README states it is **semi-abandoned and in a non-working state**. We should verify if it works or if we need to fix it/find an alternative.

